window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The final installment of the bestselling paranormal/urban fantasy romance from Sadie Kincaid comes </b><b><i>Bound in Blood</i></b><b>.</b></p> <p>But if the chosen one can slay the three-headed dragon—if the untamable beast does kneel at its new master’s feet, and the light is tempted back from the darkness, then they shall awaken the protector of man. And the sun must swallow the shadows to bring a balance that reigns through the ages.</p> <p>When the lines between good and evil grow increasingly blurred, it becomes impossible to distinguish the heroes from the villains. Ophelia Hart must call on powers old and new to save her fated mates and to stop darkness from consuming the world. </p> <p>Promises will be made. Oaths will be sworn and secrets revealed. And those who are bound in blood have no option but to fight until the end.</p> <p>A war is coming. And everyone must choose a side.</p>"; 
